<p>Hello <%= @attendee.name%>,</p>
<br>
<p>You've signed up to the following events at the CodeCore lunch and learns!</p>
<% if @has_seat_events.any?%>
  <p>You have seats for the following events:</p>
  <% @has_seat_events.each do |event| %>
    <p>Event: <%= event.title %> featuring <%= event.speaker %></p>
    <p>Date: <%= formatted_date(event.date)%> </p>
    <p>Time: <%= formatted_time(event.date)%> </p>
    <br>  
  <% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @waitlist_events.any?%>
  <p>You are waitlisted on the following events:</p>
  <% @waitlist_events.each do |event| %>
    <p>Event: <%= event.title %> featuring <%= event.speaker %></p>
    <p>Date: <%= formatted_date(event.date)%> </p>
    <p>Time: <%= formatted_time(event.date)%> </p>
    <br>  
  <% end %>
  <p>You will be notified if a spot opens up in any of these events.</p>
<% end %>
<p>Thanks for signing up. Lunch and beverages will be provided of course!</p>
<p>Please feel free to email us if you have any questions or concerns:</p>
<a href="mailto:mirko@codecore.ca?Subject=CodeCore%20Events" target="_top">mirko@codecore.ca</a>
<br>
<p><a href="http://www.codecore.ca">CodeCore.ca</a></p>
<br>
<p>Best regards,</p>
<p>inaugural CodeCore students!</p>